<h1 class="title">Kvmcli V0.9
<br />
<span class="subtitle">Introducing New Features in kvmcli v0.9</span>
</h1>
<div id="table-of-contents">
<h2>Table of Contents</h2>
<div id="text-table-of-contents">
<ul>
<li><a href="#orgb65c219">1. Improvements and Features in v0.9</a>
<ul>
<li><a href="#org0630fb8">1.1. Multiprocessing</a></li>
<li><a href="#orge7360e1">1.2. New option <code>kvmcli --init</code></a></li>
